{"tid":1354370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你老味上環元朗我睇曬","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T18:16:49.000Z","uid":57274,"like":177,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ec648b9f276b2b8fad2bcb0c18210fa19eb2ea19","tid":1354370,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，上環同元朗一樣重要呀！屌撚曬你地班五毛三毛分化狗，係咁出post揀邊企</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家係元朗鄉黑關注度高啲，但唔代表我地放棄原本對準政權嘅港島戰線！<br />\n<br />\n既然港共玩聲東擊西，開多條鄉黑戰線出黎嚇鳩我地，何不食住條水，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">趁此良機去除鄉黑之患，順手成立民間自衛隊，教曉大眾習武嘅重要性？</span><br />\n<br />\n根除鄉黑之患後，藍絲如蟻，港共亦少隊援兵突然血腥廝殺，和理非更加唔洗怕。亦正如有師兄話齋，元朗一役可能會吸咗唔少和理非新人，甚至中立人士出黎，但佢地係未夠能力參與如元朗嘅武力抗爭，之後必定要繼續原本嘅港島戰線，擴大我地嘅人數。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雙線發展係兩邊都重要，唔係側重/捨棄任何一邊。請大家繼續follow up港島受傷義士，亦準備好27,28嘅光復元朗！</span>呢個係一個好好嘅機會叫大家學識習武自衛，令勇武變主流。合力搞掂鄉黑，再對準政權大大力抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a6c1b73274e2cdad608c4672f0e2047585e9e3a5","tid":1354370,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f4f7e52b89bc21ebbd72e8f53cd9454c228f68","tid":1354370,"uid":23707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFqibUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFqibUD.jpg&h=ebc0d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRtS0NX.jpg\" data-t